\q1 
\v 1 Oh Nkulunkulu, wena engikudumisayo,
\q2 ungali ulokhu uthule,
\q1 
\v 2 ngoba abantu ababi abalenkohliso
\q2 bayivulile imilomo yabo bekhuluma ngami;
\q2 bakhuluma bengigcona ngendimi zabo zamanga.
\q1 
\v 3 Bangihonqolozela ngamazwi enzondo;
\q2 bayangisukela nje kungelasizatho.
\q1 
\v 4 Ukubathanda kwami bakuphindisela ngokungisola,
\q2 kodwa ngingumuntu womkhuleko.
\q1 
\v 5 Bangiphindisela okuhle ngokubi,
\q2 langenzondo ukubathanda kwami.
\b
\q1 
\v 6 Bathi, “Khethani umuntu omubi ozamelana laye;
\q2 ombeka icala kame kwesokunene sakhe.
\q1 
\v 7 Nxa esethonisiswa kafunyanwe elecala,
\q2 futhi sengathi imikhuleko yakhe ingamlahla.
\q1 
\v 8 Sengathi insuku zakhe zingabazilutshwana;
\q2 kakube lomunye ozathatha isikhundla sakhe sobukhokheli.
\q1 
\v 9 Sengathi abantwabakhe bangaba zintandane
\q2 lomkakhe abe ngumfelokazi.
\q1 
\v 10 Sengathi abantwabakhe bangaba zinzulane zeziceli;
\q2 sengathi bangaxotshwa emizini yabo esingamanxiwa.
\q1 
\v 11 Sengathi lowo aboleke kuye angamemuka konke alakho;
\q2 sengathi labezizweni bangaphanga izithelo zamandla akhe.
\q1 
\v 12 Akungabikhona omenzela umusa
\q2 loba ozwela izintandane zakhe.
\q1 
\v 13 Sengathi izizukulwane zakhe zingaphela,
\q2 amabizo abo esulwe esizukulwaneni esilandelayo.
\q1 
\v 14 Sengathi ububi bukayise bungakhunjulwa phambi \nd kukaThixo\nd*,
\q2 sengathi isono sikanina singacitshi lanini.
\q1 
\v 15 Sengathi izono zabo zingahlala zisobala phambi \nd kukaThixo\nd*,
\q2 ukuze aphelise du ukukhunjulwa kwabo emhlabeni.
\b
\q1 
\v 16 Ngoba kazange akhumbule ukwenza umusa
\q2 kodwa wabazingelela ukufa abayanga
\q2 labaswelayo labadabukileyo enhliziyweni.
\q1 
\v 17 Wayekuthanda ukwethesa isithuko,
\q2 sengathi singehlela kuye.
\q1 Wayengakuthandi ukubusisa
\q2 sengathi kungaba khatshana laye.
\q1 
\v 18 Wayevunula ukuthuka njengesigqoko;
\q2 kwangena emzimbeni wakhe njengamanzi,
\q2 emathanjeni akhe njengamafutha.
\q1 
\v 19 Sengathi kungaba njengengubo athandelwe ngayo
\q2 njengebhanti abotshwe ngalo lanini.”
\q1 
\v 20 Sengathi lokhu kungaba yisijeziso \nd sikaThixo\nd* kulabo abangethesa amacala,
