\v 3 Inotho lenzuzo kusendlini yakhe,
\q2 lokulunga kwakhe kumi laphakade.
\q1 
\v 4 Lasebumnyameni kuyavela ukukhanya kwabaqotho,
\q2 emuntwini olomusa, olesihawu lolungileyo.
\q1 
\v 5 Ubuhle buzakwehlela kuye ophanayo loweboleka ekhululekile,
