\q1 
\v 7 Akayikwesaba imibiko emibi;
\q2 inhliziyo yakhe ichumile, yethembele \nd kuThixo\nd*.
\q1 
\v 8 Inhliziyo yakhe ikhululekile, akalakwesaba;
